Class Patient

Object
User
Patient
public class Patient extends User
Represents a patient in the medical system, with personal information, contact details, medical records, and a list of appointments.
Since:
2024-10-27
Version:
4.7

  • Constructor Details

    • Patient

      public Patient(String name, String id, String password, Role role, Gender gender, BloodType bloodType, String phoneNo, String emailAddress, String dateOfBirth, List<String> treatments, List<String> diagnosis)
      Constructs a Patient object with specified personal and contact details, as well as an initial diagnosis and treatment history.
      Parameters:
      name - the patient's name
      id - the patient's unique identifier
      password - the patient's password
      role - the role of the user (should be PATIENT)
      gender - the patient's gender
      bloodType - the patient's blood type
      phoneNo - the patient's phone number
      emailAddress - the patient's email address
      dateOfBirth - the patient's date of birth
      treatments - initial treatments in the patient's medical record
      diagnosis - initial diagnosis in the patient's medical record
